org.sd.text.radixtree
Interface ValueMerger<T>

public interface ValueMerger<T>

An interface for resolving conflicts while building a radix tree.

This will be called in the event that there is an exact match to an existing "real" node being added to the trie.

Author:
Spence Koehler
